name: Full moon
summary: The next full moon, occurring on November 15, 2024, is significant as it is the last of four consecutive supermoons. This supermoon, also known as the Beaver Moon, will be particularly notable for its proximity to the Pleiades star cluster, known as the "Seven Sisters." The full moon in November is traditionally called the Beaver Moon, as it corresponds with the time when beavers begin to prepare for winter. This celestial event is expected to be visible worldwide and will be the final supermoon of the year. Astrologically, the full moon in Taurus is said to bring about chaotic and unexpected changes, while horoscopes suggest that it will impact different zodiac signs in various ways.

name: UAP
summary: Recent news articles indicate heightened interest and scrutiny regarding Unidentified Aerial Phenomena (UAPs). The House Oversight Committee held a hearing, where experts testified about alleged secret UAP programs run by the U.S. Witnesses, including former NASA official Michael Gold, shared their accounts and recommendations for congressional action. The hearing revealed that UAPs are considered real, and lawmakers are urging the Pentagon to enhance transparency in ongoing investigations. Additionally, Avi Loeb, a renowned physicist, provided his statement on UAPs, emphasizing their existence and the need for scientific exploration. Witnesses also raised concerns about alleged government efforts to suppress information on UFOs. The hearing underscored the growing public interest and pressure on lawmakers and government agencies to provide answers, promote transparency, and address the topic of UAPs more openly.
